3ad6217bebc04","tid":587032,"uid":24814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf6e1fea58a6d62122ca3f7a5e0584a7494dda75","tid":587032,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"末日出去搵食物先係真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"搵食物 學種田 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係幾多嘢食都會有食哂嘅一日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"末日梗係出去搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdadb6d5778ef519c20f1c968961a35250a58038","tid":587032,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:29:21.000Z","msg":"沙甸魚"},{"pid":"44458b1bc9f1c225527d41318df0fe6892b1e0c3","tid":587032,"uid":54733,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"無論發生咩事都唔洗驚<br />\n要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea113b633a3ab413b245a66cffc9dff563ec3fe8","tid":587032,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>末日出去搵食物先係真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>搵食物 學種田 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係幾多嘢食都會有食哂嘅一日</blockquote><br />\n種完比人搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市區邊有地方種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548fdd86777fbb23104e880044a1527b93e3d444","tid":587032,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>末日出去搵食物先係真男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>搵食物 學種田 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係幾多嘢食都會有食哂嘅一日</blockquote><br />\n種完比人搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市區邊有地方種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天台"},{"pid":"2ce845ef2701f30a0b7c2f41a560ab6f586b5f3e","tid":587032,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T06:49:03.000Z","msg":"末日題材係一個好商機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}